<view class="setup-page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-title">首次设置</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">只保存在本地，不上传。先填个大概月薪，后面可改。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="setup-card">
    <view class="card-tag">本地保存</view>

    <view class="field-label">月薪（大概）</view>
    <view class="salary-input-wrap">
      <view class="salary-prefix">¥</view>
      <input
        class="salary-input"
        type="digit"
        placeholder="输入你那微薄的薪水..."
        placeholder-class="salary-placeholder"
        bindinput="onSalaryInput"
        value="{{monthlySalary}}"
      />
    </view>

    <view class="field-tip">用于估算今天回血多少，不会上传。</view>

    <view class="start-btn" bindtap="saveConfig">保存并开始打工</view>

    <view class="footer-tip">进入后可以继续完善工作日、上下班时间、午休等规则。</view>
  </view>
</view>
